A system supplying power to operate the anchor windlasses and other anchoring equipment.;
[C153] A system supplying mechanical power to operate the anchor windlasses and other anchoring equipment.;
[E201] A system supplying electric power to operate the anchor windlasses and other anchoring equipment.;
[S201] A system supplying hydraulic power to operate the anchor windlasses and other anchoring equipment.;
[S202] A system supplying pneumatic power to operate the anchor windlasses and other anchoring equipment.

A system supplying power to operate the position mooring windlasses and other anchoring equipment.;
[C153] A system supplying mechanical power to operate the position mooring windlasses and other anchoring equipment.;
[E201] A system supplying electric power to operate the position mooring windlasses and other anchoring equipment.;
[S201] A system supplying hydraulic power to operate the position mooring windlasses and other anchoring equipment.;
[S202] A system supplying pneumatic power to operate the position mooring windlasses and other anchoring equipment.

Line segments (chain, steel wire rope or fibre rope) that together with the connecting elements transfer tensile forces between the vessel and the anchor.;
[C971] Chain segments that together with the connecting elements  transfer tensile forces between the vessel and the anchor.;
[C972] Steel wire rope segments that together with the connecting elements  transfer tensile forces between the vessel and the anchor.;
[C973] Fibre rope segments that together with the connecting elements  transfer tensile forces between the vessel and the anchor.

Devices providing buoyancy to the position mooring line.;
[H201] Tanks providing buoyancy to the position mooring line.;
[M51] Materials providing buoyancy to the position mooring line.
